Interface ICompanyRep

All Superinterfaces:
IUser
All Known Implementing Classes:
CompanyRep
public interface ICompanyRep extends IUser
Company representative-specific interface extending IUser. This interface exposes operations and attributes unique to company representatives, supporting the Interface Segregation Principle by ensuring other user types do not depend on unnecessary methods.
